To use it in linux or mac mahinces:

In TERMINAL
{if pip3 is not installed}Install pip3 by 'sudo apt install python3-pip' 
{if PyPDF2 is not installed}Type 'pip3 install PyPDF2'
Type 'python3 merger.py <name of your pdf.pdf>'


To use it in Windows mahinces:

Is CMD 
Install python3 by google and install it
{if PyPDF2 is not installed}Type 'pip install PyPDF2'
Type 'python merger.py <name of your pdf.pdf>'
